{"tid":1416450,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"傳藍衫漢荃灣聚集、毆市民至頭破血流　田北辰引述警方指已知悉","createTime":"2019-08-05T15:04:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T18:25:31.000Z","uid":212249,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f56d92d24535471f0dab5fb3bfb71cc61ddbd3c9","tid":1416450,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:04:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/bluetee-03_gOTBa_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fbluetee-03_gOTBa_1200x0.png&h=6ac9d556&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網上流傳相片及片段，顯示今晚（5日）有身穿藍衣的男子在荃灣聚集。立法會議員田北辰在 FB 發帖，稱自己已向警方表示，荃灣有白衣及藍衣人士聚集，警方亦回覆已收到有關信息。田北辰表示：「如果仲係冇警察，我一定追究。」<br />\n<br />\n今日網上流傳片段，有市民拍攝到今晚有身穿藍色、寫有「I ❤ 香港」 T-恤、手持疑似鐵通的男子在荃灣力生路德圍一帶出沒，另外亦有相片拍攝到，有市民懷疑被打至頭破血流。<br />\n<br />\n亦有另一段片段拍攝到，有十數名藍衣男子被身穿黑衣的示威者趕走。<br />\n<br />\n有目擊者向《立場》記者表示，當時有藍衣人突然用棍扑向他朋友的頭部，他的朋友頓時頭破血流。而目擊者亦在荃灣沙咀道公園，發現有一大箱全新、寫有「I ❤ 香港」 的藍色T-恤。T-恤紙箱上的收件地址顯示為尖沙咀棉登徑1號 19樓一個單位。<br />\n<br />\n田北辰 Michael Tien<br />\n約 1 小時前<br />\n荃灣白衣同藍衣人聚集，我已經同警方講咗，佢哋話收到，如果仲係冇警察，我一定追究。<br />\n各位，有咩消息繼續同我講，未能一一回覆，但我同我助理會睇到，保證一定處理！<br />\n<br />\n更新：好多市民問黑衣人，我有講，警方資料比我更詳盡，我重點係佢哋未必有嘅資料。呢個時間，我就唔分咩顏色，唉。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/8-5-%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81-%E5%82%B3%E8%97%8D%E8%A1%AB%E6%BC%A2%E8%8D%83%E7%81%A3%E8%81%9A%E9%9B%86-%E6%AF%86%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E8%87%B3%E9%A0%AD%E7%A0%B4%E8%A1%80%E6%B5%81-%E7%94%B0%E5%8C%97%E8%BE%B0%E5%BC%95%E8%BF%B0%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E6%8C%87%E5%B7%B2%E7%9F%A5%E6%82%89/?fbclid=IwAR1YzeD9hPpLzzi6MBjvBK7OKCjDoxP58-YrGYOMe4FvetVNtYhi1eJPjlA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F8-5-%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581-%25E5%2582%25B3%25E8%2597%258D%25E8%25A1%25AB%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%258D%2583%25E7%2581%25A3%25E8%2581%259A%25E9%259B%2586-%25E6%25AF%2586%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%25B0%2591%25E8%2587%25B3%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E7%25A0%25B4%25E8%25A1%2580%25E6%25B5%2581-%25E7%2594%25B0%25E5%258C%2597%25E8%25BE%25B0%25E5%25BC%2595%25E8%25BF%25B0%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%258C%2587%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E7%259F%25A5%25E6%2582%2589%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1YzeD9hPpLzzi6MBjvBK7OKCjDoxP58-YrGYOMe4FvetVNtYhi1eJPjlA&d=ERzkPk9H60tcRIh4HMRTrvQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=b0304249\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F8-5-%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581-%25E5%2582%25B3%25E8%2597%258D%25E8%25A1%25AB%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%258D%2583%25E7%2581%25A3%25E8%2581%259A%25E9%259B%2586-%25E6%25AF%2586%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%25B0%2591%25E8%2587%25B3%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E7%25A0%25B4%25E8%25A1%2580%25E6%25B5%2581-%25E7%2594%25B0%25E5%258C%2597%25E8%25BE%25B0%25E5%25BC%2595%25E8%25BF%25B0%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%258C%2587%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E7%259F%25A5%25E6%2582%2589%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1YzeD9hPpLzzi6MBjvBK7OKCjDoxP58-YrGYOMe4FvetVNtYhi1eJPjlA&h=868aaa2c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/8-5-%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81-%E5%82%B3%E8%97%8D%E8%A1%AB%E6%BC%A2%E8%8D%83%E7%81%A3%E8%81%9A%E9%9B%86-%E6%AF%86%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E8%87%B3%E9%A0%AD%E7%A0%B4%E8%A1%80%E6%B5%81-%E7%94%B0%E5%8C%97%E8%BE%B0%E5%BC%95%E8%BF%B0%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E6%8C%87%E5%B7%B2%E7%9F%A5%E6%82%89/?fbclid=IwAR1YzeD9hPpLzzi6MBjvBK7OKCjDoxP58-YrGYOMe4FvetVNtYhi1eJPjlA</a>"},{"pid":"727ad481251f4e3b1b7c585363c6fe80dd35aa0d","tid":1416450,"uid":51583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:05:48.000Z","msg":"等睇結果"},{"pid":"701d80c791628f4f87db2ce1fe561ade3de0ea9f","tid":1416450,"uid":156203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:06:04.000Z","msg":"區選近了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ef82f67c4cf7f2db3470c4ef49ac9ecdf6ad110","tid":1416450,"uid":271857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:08:11.000Z","msg":"黑社會治港。"},{"pid":"a70dc4b836ecef48b184d362d82798412d8a418e","tid":1416450,"uid":288351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:09:32.000Z","msg":"擇個日子開波啦。鬼撚鼠鼠。d黑社會真癈"},{"pid":"cd56b72e5f8e305b5528957bd5aed0196800ebe0","tid":1416450,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:17:52.000Z","msg":"田少助攻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cdeda0e686c6d6a80f11275d3cbdc291beed951","tid":1416450,"uid":216789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:19:35.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"},{"pid":"346715ed6728109f765bb9f8bb8567ea71a59b9b","tid":1416450,"uid":1053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"701d80c791628f4f87db2ce1fe561ade3de0ea9f","tid":1416450,"uid":156203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:06:04.000Z","msg":"區選近了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:47:39.000Z","msg":"佢本身都贏硬啦<br />\n中產區好buy佢有牙力幫地區fight到好多野"},{"pid":"5cab1c5f263f9c365dd2ed752657e2ba98ce73c7","tid":1416450,"uid":210682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:25:31.000Z","msg":"佢會唔會博出位博到做咗泛民？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}